<h2>Who We Are</h2>

<p class="padt1">In a crowded market, Janatec stands apart from competitors thanks to our deep understanding of the industries in which we work, ability to deliver within the agreed price and schedule, international reach supported by local engagement, and an <span class="hilite1">innovative approach to the use of technology to drive business success.</span></p>

<p>Our business is structured around six core service offerings: web-based solutions, internet strategy, product engineering, enterprise integration, e-government, and business consulting.</p>
<p>This industry focus means that <span class="hilite2">our services and solutions are tailored to help solve our client's most pressing challenges day in and day out.</span> Using their industry expertise and strong business and technology insights, we deliver solutions that enable them to build and maintain leadership positions in their respective markets.</p>
<p>Our clients demand world-class business and technology services and we are committed to exceeding their expectations.</p>
